    "In Sect. 3, we present our proposed dimensions, explaining how we group the recent works in the categories of each dimension.",
    "In Sect. 4, we discuss the trends that we found in the literature, and, driven by the proposed dimensions, we propose possible research directions in this research area.",
    "We finalize the paper with some conclusions in Sect. 5.",
    "BackgroundIn this section, we first provide the necessary background on multi-agent reinforcement learning.",
    "Then, we show how multi-agent reinforcement learning can be extended to consider communication between agents."
